{"tid":2044463,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支持香港製造品牌","createTime":"2020-05-31T06:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T13:13:40.000Z","uid":252031,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"df9784dd3fd5d859db244e778dcc97dc94ee5510","tid":2044463,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T06:19:27.000Z","msg":"雖然香港製造業式微咗好耐，但其實香港仲有d自家品牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁小弟參考咗以前有心人整嘅一份資料，重新按唔同行業list咗啲香港品牌或者自家製嘅產品<br />\n但係呢啲鋪我鄭係識幾間係黃嘅，希望大家幫手望一望幫手分黃藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他無表態個啲,都支持下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/15f2xUwJmkeFHAZT2_Htg_DVrny8ONiYAx9o_FBZH9Pg/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F15f2xUwJmkeFHAZT2_Htg_DVrny8ONiYAx9o_FBZH9Pg%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdK9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=92f41571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/15f2xUwJmkeFHAZT2_Htg_DVrny8ONiYAx9o_FBZH9Pg/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n資料參考<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1LrEjqK9VzHA8Irr0Bfg3kQjewU_TYWQxLnWoc74Rpmo/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1LrEjqK9VzHA8Irr0Bfg3kQjewU_TYWQxLnWoc74Rpmo%2Fedit&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdK9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=8f0fede7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1LrEjqK9VzHA8Irr0Bfg3kQjewU_TYWQxLnWoc74Rpmo/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n另外都希望大家多啲撐下膳心同龍門嘅手足Product<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba325b60d6125dace03bbffb47e50cfa9e561ed4","tid":2044463,"uid":252031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T06:20:25.000Z","msg":"香港黑警4日內死咗3個<br />\n祝早日